Step 1: Download and Install JDK

Step 2: Set the path
C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_191\bin

Step 3:
This PC->right click -> Advanced system settings->environment variables->
path->new ->paste your path ->click on OK

Step 4: Open your CMD and type javac

javac->java compiler[JDK]

jdk -version

Step 5: Download and Install Eclipse

Step 6:Select Java EE web developers

=> Java is a case sensitive Language

Data Types:

int -> numeric value

float -> decimal

char -> character

double -> decimal

boolean -> true,false

String -> Any data

